N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 ยง 420.5 - State reimbursement

State Regulations

Expenditures by an authorized agency for the care and
maintenance of a child subject to referral to the State Adoption Service under
this Part will not be subject to State reimbursement unless the agency has
complied with the requirements of this Part. Notes
